<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٣٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{دَائِبَينَ}</span> ... جَارِيَيْنِ لَا يَفْتُرَانِ وَلَا يَتَوَقَّفَانِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٣٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَهْوِي إِلَيْهِمْ}</span> ... تَمِيلُ إِلَيْهِمْ، وَتَحِنُّ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٤٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَشْخَصُ}</span> ... تَرْتَفِعُ عُيُونُهُمْ فِيهِ، وَلَا تَغْمَضُ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٤٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُهْطِعِينَ}</span> ... مُسْرِعِينَ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٤٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُقْنِعِي رُؤُوسِهِمْ}</span> ... رَافِعِي رُؤُوسِهِمْ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٤٣)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَأَفْئِدَتُهُمْ هَوَاءٌ}</span> ... قُلُوبُهُمْ خَالِيَةٌ مِنْ شِدَّةِ الهَوْلِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٤٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَبَرَزُوا}</span> ... خَرَجُوا ظَاهِرِينَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٤٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مُّقَرَّنِينَ فِي الأَصْفَادِ}</span> ... مُقَيَّدِينَ بِالقُيُودِ، قَدْ قُرِنَتْ أَيْدِيهِمْ وَأَرْجُلُهُمْ بِالسَّلَاسِلِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٥٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَرَابِيلُهُمْ}</span> ... ثِيَابُهُمْ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(٥٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قَطِرَانٍ}</span> ... مَادَّةٍ شَدِيدَةِ الِاشْتِعَالِ، تُشْبِهُ الزِّفْتَ، سَوْدَاءِ اللَّوْنِ مُنْتِنَةِ الرِّيحِ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٥٠)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَتَغْشَى}</span> ... تَعْلُو، وَتَلْفَحُ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>